  "notes": "Live 2026-04 Shopify parity for orderCustomerSet and orderCustomerRemove error-path fidelity. Replay creates customers, B2B company/contact setup, B2B and non-B2B orders, cancels the non-B2B order through the public request surface, then verifies happy set/remove, not-found branches, B2B no-role set rejection, B2B remove rejection, and cancelled non-B2B remove success without runtime Shopify writes."
